description: The Sevrin 4 Men's shoe is a dark burgundy shoe with a suede upper, black trim, and contrasting white solid rubber sole. These have Ortholite insoles, which in addition to creating a highly cushioned, comfortable footbed, also reduces any bad odours and works to prevent any fungus from forming. Featuring embroidered Lacoste text on the top of the tongue, and a small metal crocodile on the side, each shoe shows off the Lacoste brand. In stock, ready to buy from Cloggs.

Created from suede leather and a contrasting rubber sole, the Millard Men's shoe in Dark Brown has a cushioned insole, which provides premium comfort for extended periods of wear. These and other Lacoste men's shoes are available to buy from Cloggs.

The Lacoste Clavel 17 Men's shoe in Dark Blue has a stylish and sleek look, providing great comfort too. The upper is made from Nubuck, which is a premium and long-lasting type of leather with a velvety look and feel, contrasting with the black/white striped trim, and durable white rubber sole. They have a 3-hole lace up design, complete with blue laces. Available in Dark Blue from Cloggs.

Made from a mix of real leather and suede, these dark brown Lacoste Sherbrooke Hi Men's shoes have a stylish textured upper and a three-hole lace up closure, giving a desert shoe feel. The solid rubber sole gives a firm feel when walking, and is sewn into the leather/suede upper part of the shoe. A small Lacoste crocodile is neatly sewn to the outer leather. These would suit an outfit with denim jeans, or even a more formal look, and are available with free UK delivery from Cloggs.

Available in Dark Brown, the Clavel 17 Men's shoe by Lacoste has an upper made from Nubuck; a premium type of leather which has a soft, velvety feel. The dark brown Nubuck upper contrasts with the white rubber sole and black/white trim. These have a 3-hole lace up design, with brown laces. To offer good grip, these have a textured black rubber sole. Available in Dark Brown from Cloggs.

This Lacoste Ampthill Men's high-top shoe in the Black Terra design features blue laces which contrast with the black design. Showcasing the crocodile on the side which stands out from the rest of the black shoe, the Lacoste branding is clearly visible. Available with free  next day UK delivery from Cloggs.

description: The Showcourt Women's shoe from Lacoste is an all-white shoe, with a leather upper neatly stitched to a white rubber sole, textured to offer the best possible grip. These feature a 7-hole lace-up closure, complete with white laces. To compliment the all-white design,  the green Lacoste crocodile is embroidered on the outer side of each shoe. Available to order from Cloggs, with free UK delivery.

Lacoste produced their first tennis shoe back in 1985. Ever since, they've kept to their original roots, creating timeless classic shoes for all. With a grey textile upper and white rubber sole, these Carnaby Women's Grey Evo Marl shoes by Lacoste are no exception, and  have a lightweight and comfortable design - perfect for use as an active shoe. The Ortholite insole offers great comfort, whilst actively preventing odours and fungus from forming. These are complete with an embroidered crocodile on the side of each shoe, grey tab at  the rear of the shoe also featuring the Lacoste crocodile, and a seven-hole lace-up closure. Free UK delivery available from Cloggs.
